{"tid":283041,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙南部6日畢業旅行不負責任遊記","createTime":"2017-06-13T22:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T20:20:46.000Z","uid":32932,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7d2d50d639c59821729b9ae1a93e4dbb7986a55","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:34:49.000Z","msg":"話說我喺5月28至6月3日就去左西班牙南部旅行。今次係我第2次去西班牙，上年去左西班牙嘅Seville同Barcelona，之後好鍾意Seville，好鍾意西班牙南部啲建築同埋啲人好熱情，雖然發生咗啲非常唔開心嘅事，但始終都係好鍾意Seville。而Barcelona可能因為我自己唔睇波，所以冇咩特別感覺，大城市一個。<br />\n<br />\n返到香港之後，一直好遺憾冇去西班牙南部嘅白色山城。今年因為要去摩洛哥嘅關係喺5月就再去左一次西班牙，終於去到好想去白色山城。之前去左一次西班牙，但覺得打遊記實在好痛苦，打一堆嘢好似得自己自high咁，又唔多人睇，所以上次打到半路就放棄左。不過今次希望可以係自己記憶慢慢消失之前畀自己做個紀錄。大家鍾意嘅畀個正評支持下我龜速打遊記啦。<br />\n<br />\n利申：去西班牙之前其實我冇做research，淨係book左d車飛同hostel，景點全部唔知。所以如果跟住我個遊記去而中伏的話唔好問候我屋企人啊，我不負責任架。"},{"pid":"3920999589e215a71c3e92a44a089fbcd0f0c7c7","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:35:16.000Z","msg":"29/5: 因為delay，1am抵達西班牙南部城市Malaga。12nn搭車去Granada。<br />\n30/5: Granada<br />\n31/5: 3pm離開Granada，搭車去Cordoba<br />\n1/6: 5pm離開Cordoba，去Ronda<br />\n2/6: 1:30pm離開Ronda，返Malaga<br />\n3/6: 1:30離開Malaga，搭船去Morocco<br />\n29/5: 因為delay，1am抵達西班牙南部城市Malaga。12nn搭車去Granada。<br />\n30/5: Granada<br />\n31/5: 3pm離開Granada，搭車去Cordoba<br />\n1/6: 5pm離開Cordoba，去Ronda<br />\n2/6: 1:30pm離開Ronda，返Malaga<br />\n3/6: 1:30離開Malaga，搭船去Morocco"},{"pid":"adc09971226836e614e50e9243648bb4f78a6b74","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:36:07.000Z","msg":"屌 上面copy重覆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b549cea90bea82c14b18ff05a5740bd7c4141280","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:38:04.000Z","msg":"29/5 <br />\n<br />\n       我係瑞典Stockholm搭Norwegian airline過去西班牙南部最大嘅城市，1am先到西班牙。個機場半夜冇車去市區，一定要搭的士或者Call車。本身用Norwegian嘅wifi download咗個西班牙call車app，諗住到左可以call車。點知個機場冇wifi，so9sad。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n       為左避免唔知畀的士司機車去邊，我一向一係搭metro或者巴士，唔識搭車就行路。但今次拖喼，所以就一定要搭的士。Hostel本身話由機場搭的士過去要25歐，我見深夜可能有附加費就預30歐左右。<br />\n<br />\n       我一上車個司機就set做8歐起標，一路諗緊佢係咪亂收我錢。我同個司機又雞同鴨講咁，佢係咁同我講西班牙文，我一直話我唔識。上左的士之後，我就扮同人講: Hi, I&rsquo;m on my way. I&rsquo;m on the taxi。之後又一直開住google map，又show下畀的士司機，等佢唔好兜我路呃錢。最後車費係22歐！仲平過hostel講個價！個司機仲好好禮貌同我講byebye，我個下好內疚，好人當賊辦。"},{"pid":"528b28883126446cdd6982b25f80ba2211ca41c5","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/064157_34599b6d09590156b8200e3e0b60fdd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F064157_34599b6d09590156b8200e3e0b60fdd3.jpg&h=4596255f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/064241_cfa7714ca6eff5dece6747fb67a99c93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F064241_cfa7714ca6eff5dece6747fb67a99c93.jpg&h=08d8f60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺飛機上面睇到日落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff23935d9e619c927fc00010c1be5f38a4b011ff","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T22:55:26.000Z","msg":"第一晚喺Malaga住喺The Lights Hostel（10人Mixed Dorm，16歐）。我選擇呢間hostel因為佢地可以免費寄存行李喺佢地到五日，同埋有24小時check-in。去到Hostel settle down已經3am左右，之後廢事嘈醒全世界就諗住直接訓，但hostel係自己揀床，我就好辛苦咁爬左上床到，仲要嘈醒左其他人，點知發現我爬左上個男人張床:0)。最後好柒咁碌返落下面，又爬上第2張床上格，又嘈醒左下面條友，對唔住啊cryyyy。<br />\n<br />\n本身book左8am巴士去Granada，最後我起身個陣已經9點:0)，仲要未執行李、未沖涼洗頭。最後再買左12nn車飛，又跌10歐。"},{"pid":"4d14d9099370966515ea4f02ec04e04319717d26","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T23:02:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.chinese.hostelworld.com/hosteldetails.php/The-Lights-Hostel/malajia/90359?dateFrom=2017-06-15&amp;dateTo=2017-06-18&amp;number_of_guests=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinese.hostelworld.com%2Fhosteldetails.php%2FThe-Lights-Hostel%2Fmalajia%2F90359%3FdateFrom%3D2017-06-15%26dateTo%3D2017-06-18%26number_of_guests%3D2&d=sOdAtgzxSNOGM087bcBtqP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c1e1ffda\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinese.hostelworld.com/hosteldetails.php/The-Lights-Hostel/malajia/90359?dateFrom=2017-06-15&amp;dateTo=2017-06-18&amp;number_of_guests=2</a><br />\n<br />\n呢間Hostel位置都唔錯，hostel有電梯搭，唔洗搬行李上樓梯，<br />\nd staff幾nice同埋佢地好熟悉Malaga同埋去其他城市既交通，教我點去搭船摩洛哥，有晒去唔同地方既巴士既時間表，<br />\n同埋張床有簾有安全感，<br />\n最好就係可以store行李，16歐訓一晚，免費store5日行李，租locker都要呢個價錢啦<br />\n<br />\n不過唔好在冇冷氣，同埋見到hostel咁多評語就知Hostel都有返咁上下歷史，<br />\n同埋間Hostel唔多靚，無咩特色，我自己偏好靚既Hostel"},{"pid":"d2e0560fa0f683bf570f0ce057060936ed819291","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T23:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/070321_5e0d79982e94d4d3a47d8b61c5f78c62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F070321_5e0d79982e94d4d3a47d8b61c5f78c62.jpg&h=ef79a57a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/070335_53519874c47a8c5b7e68f385ee62bcbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F070335_53519874c47a8c5b7e68f385ee62bcbc.jpg&h=2c7c7d77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/070346_8c3598214578ff7e8633af263c954e62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F070346_8c3598214578ff7e8633af263c954e62.jpg&h=b8ec7aac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/070400_e2ed8606d9027906a6170bd667ffc392.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F070400_e2ed8606d9027906a6170bd667ffc392.jpg&h=14d0a1c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nbtw Malaga周圍都係street art<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為趕住去Granada，所以冇時間參觀Malaga，之後會再講下Malaga"},{"pid":"387c58ab8660170412406dd603f2c945858a34a1","tid":283041,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T23:34:39.000Z","msg":"支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我d遊記都無人睇<br />\n純粹自high同比個回憶自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fffbad6b461ea968bd191916d26244dae6d58c","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T23:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我d遊記都無人睇<br />\n純粹自high同比個回憶自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地互相支持啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"080532fcc887cc7de6337bea5b4fbe5078d44bf6","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T00:29:28.000Z","msg":"前面廢話有啲多，不過後面廢話一樣多<br />\n但而家開始會多d圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一去到巴士站，仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔記得check定點去間hostel tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。一落車見到一對香港人情侶就去搭嗲，叫佢地幫我check下行去hostel要行幾耐，因為我冇買上網卡，佢地幫我check到要行40分鐘。最後同佢地夾左的士去我住既hostel附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/081619_6b0a88b5301f949fd68e9e2001b00e67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F081619_6b0a88b5301f949fd68e9e2001b00e67.jpg&h=924711fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅色係一座山，叫阿爾拜辛區 <br />\n藍色又係另一座山，喺Granada最重要嘅景點Alhambra嘅所在地<br />\n綠地係新城區，冇咩特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有local形容: not very interesting，same as other cities<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你hostel/hotel喺阿爾拜辛區，但清晨5點要上Albambra嘅話，因為未有巴士，所以要首先碌落山再爬返上山，祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至於點解清晨要上Albambra，我下回再分解<br />\n<br />\n搭的士去到阿爾拜辛區，勁鍾意呢到，因為我好鍾意係巷弄到行，local 叫我enjoy following the map and getting lost~<br />\n不過呢到周圍都係大麻味，一邊聞住大麻味，一邊上山落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/080409_4e1f4364c896a44bfb239ac907cec2ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F080409_4e1f4364c896a44bfb239ac907cec2ae.jpg&h=7539b687&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/080412_4b363fa3dbd706e43a656bdcfb616258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F080412_4b363fa3dbd706e43a656bdcfb616258.jpg&h=38f28cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/080414_f6243b60ba9e4798a1846fef4266954a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F080414_f6243b60ba9e4798a1846fef4266954a.jpg&h=55e564eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/080417_bcd4ba79431422844685c797848d4df0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F080417_bcd4ba79431422844685c797848d4df0.jpg&h=b48079f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"240ba1e9bf276a76820a7eaa00fa6bb9af1c8e24","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T00:36:50.000Z","msg":"plan完意大利行程再繼續打，想快快手book機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bba1a243dbd2bd7381cbe18e7b7c0d674acc59","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T00:41:07.000Z","msg":"點解負評我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想睇咪上一頁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e8a40741edeb1beeb2f525c36b98028c529ff1","tid":283041,"uid":15486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T00:48:40.000Z","msg":"係seville發生左咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都有去過 好鐘意seville個種好慢既節奏"},{"pid":"78c8bc6375e12e12d4283d64ffe381906659da0a","tid":283041,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T00:50:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係seville發生左咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都有去過 好鐘意seville個種好慢既節奏</blockquote><br />\n畀阿伯抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  sad左一星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece3afd301dcfd95c2c0c5fb5169fb9e668e5a0d","tid":283041,"uid":82933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T00:59:32.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98b28fab339a52eb934a300fb5d37f546fd5bb9","tid":283041,"uid":21111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T01:25:04